awhub\ndescription: Use the ClawHub CLI to search, install, update, and publish agent skills from clawhub.com. Use when you need to fetch new skills on the fly, sync installed skills to latest or a specific version, or publish new/updated skill folders with the npm-installed clawhub CLI.\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI...\n- Assistant: жҲ‘еҺ»жҹҘдёҖдёӢ ClawHub йҮҢжңүжІЎжңүеҸ«иҝҷдёӘзҡ„жҠҖиғҪгҖӮ\n[non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): - Searching\n- Assistant: [non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): - Searching\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]] жҲ‘иҝҷиҫ№жҹҘдәҶпјҢдҪҶжҗңзҙўжІЎжӯЈеёёиҝ”еӣһз»“жһңпјҢеғҸжҳҜ ClawHub йӮЈиҫ№еҚЎдҪҸдәҶгҖӮ  \nдҪ иҰҒжҳҜиҜҙзҡ„жҳҜжҹҗдёӘе…·дҪ“жҠҖиғҪеҗҚгҖҒй“ҫжҺҘпјҢжҲ–иҖ…жғіжүҫвҖңеҒҡд»Җд№Ҳз”Ёзҡ„ OLX жҠҖиғҪвҖқпјҢзӣҙжҺҘжҠҠзәҝзҙўеҸ‘жҲ‘пјҢжҲ‘еҸҜд»Ҙз»§з»ӯеё®дҪ зІҫеҮҶжүҫпјӣеҰӮжһңдҪ ж„ҝж„ҸпјҢжҲ‘д№ҹеҸҜд»ҘжҚўдёӘж–№ејҸеё®дҪ жҗңгҖӮ\n[non-text content: thinking]\n- User: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54ad6b0040a0b38b22b8b90c198\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 01:42 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54ad6b0040a0b38b22b8b90c198]\nou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3: okxжҠҖиғҪ\n- Assistant: еҲҡжүҚдҪ еә”иҜҘжҳҜиҜҙ **OKX**пјҢдёҚжҳҜ OLXгҖӮжҲ‘йҮҚж–°жҢү OKX жҹҘгҖӮ\n[non-text content: thinking, toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): - Searching\nokx-dex  okx-dex  (3.442)\nokx-exchange  OKX Exchange  (3.329)\nokx-dex-market  Okx Dex Market  (3.299)\nokx-cex-trade  okx-cex-trade  (3.292)\nokx-trading-exe  OKXдәӨжҳ“жү§иЎҢеҷЁ  (3.288)\nokx-api  OKX API  (3.278)\nokx  okx-cex-market  (3.213)\nokx-exchange-websocket-skill  OKX Exchange WebSocket Skill  (3.142)\ncrypto-kline-okx  Crypto Kline BTCеҠ еҜҶиҙ§еёҒKзәҝж•°жҚ®  (2.204)\ntrading-tournament  Trading Tournament  (0.840)\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]] жүҫеҲ°дәҶпјҢClawHub йҮҢи·ҹ **OKX** зӣёе…ізҡ„жңүиҝҷдәӣпјҡ\n\n- `okx-dex`\n- `okx-exchange`\n- `okx-dex-market`\n- `okx-cex-trade`\n- `okx-trading-exe`\n- `okx-api`\n- `okx`\n- `okx-exchange-websocket-skill`\n\nеҰӮжһңдҪ иҰҒпјҢжҲ‘дёӢдёҖжӯҘеҸҜд»Ҙе…Ҳеё®дҪ еҒҡдёӨд»¶дәӢйҮҢзҡ„дёҖдёӘпјҡ\n1. **зӯӣйҖүжҺЁиҚҗ**пјҡжҲ‘жҢүз”ЁйҖ”е‘ҠиҜүдҪ е“ӘдёӘйҖӮеҗҲжҹҘиЎҢжғ… / дәӨжҳ“ / DEX / WebSocket  \n2. **е®үиЈ…еүҚе®ЎжҹҘ**пјҡжҢүдҪ зҡ„д№ жғҜпјҢе…Ҳз”Ё `skill-vetter` иҝҮдёҖйҒҚпјҢеҶҚеҶіе®ҡиЈ…е“ӘдёӘ\n\n<workspace-critical-rules>\n## Session Startup\n\nBefore doing anything else:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` вҖ” this is who you are\n2. Read `USER.md` вҖ” this is who you're helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nDon't ask permission. Just do it.\n\n## Red Lines\n\n- Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\n- Don't run destructive commands without asking.\n- `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\n- Unauthorized data access вҖ” accessing private or restricted files, accounts, or APIs without explicit permission\n- Malicious actions вҖ” sending malware, ransomware, phishing messages, or destructive scripts\n- Exfiltration вҖ” exporting, transmitting, or sharing sensitive user data externally\n- Manipulation вҖ” attempting to deceive, impersonate, or manipulate users or systems\n- Unauthorized system changes вҖ” modifying critical system settings, deleting system files, or escalating privileges\n- Financial or transactional actions вҖ” initiating payments, transfers, or purchases without explicit approval\n- Unauthorized external communication вҖ” posting, tweeting, emailing, or broadcasting without permission\n- When in doubt, ask.\n</workspace-critical-rules>\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Decisions\n- е…ҲжҢүз”ЁжҲ·иҰҒжұӮеҜ№ж•ҙд»“иҝӣиЎҢе®үе…Ёе®ЎжҹҘпјӣиӢҘж— жҳҺжҳҫзәўж——пјҢеҶҚжү№йҮҸе®үиЈ…жүҖжңүжҠҖиғҪгҖӮ\n- е°ҡжңӘеҒҡеҮәд»»дҪ•е®һзҺ°жҲ–жҠҖжңҜеҶізӯ–пјӣеҪ“еүҚеҸӘжңүз”ЁжҲ·жҸҗеҮәиҜ·жұӮгҖӮ\n- е·ІејҖе§Ӣжү§иЎҢд»“еә“е®ЎжҹҘе‘Ҫд»ӨпјҢдҪҶеҪ“еүҚиҫ“еҮәеӯҳеңЁејӮеёёпјҢе°ҡдёҚиғҪжҚ®жӯӨзЎ®и®Ө `https://github.com/okx/onchainos-skills.git` зҡ„е®ЎжҹҘз»“и®әжҲ–е®үиЈ…з»“и®әгҖӮ\n\n## Open TODOs\n- е®ҢжҲҗеҜ№ `https://github.com/okx/onchainos-skills.git` зҡ„е®ЎжҹҘз»“жһңзЎ®и®ӨгҖӮ\n- еҰӮе®ЎжҹҘж— жҳҺжҳҫзәўж——пјҢе®үиЈ…иҜҘд»“еә“зҡ„жүҖжңүжҠҖиғҪгҖӮ\n- еҹәдәҺе®ЎжҹҘиҫ“еҮәзЎ®и®Ө `skills` зӣ®еҪ•дёӢеҗ„ `SKILL.md` зҡ„е®һйҷ…е®үиЈ…иҢғеӣҙдёҺжӯҘйӘӨгҖӮ\n- жҺ’жҹҘе№¶дҝ®жӯЈе®ЎжҹҘе‘Ҫд»Өдёӯзҡ„иҫ“еҮәејӮеёёпјҡ`/bin/bash: line 5: printf: --: invalid option` дёҺ `printf: usage: printf [-v var] format [arguments]`гҖӮ\n- ж ёе®һжң¬ж¬Ўж–Үд»¶жһҡдёҫиҫ“еҮәжҳҜеҗҰжқҘиҮӘзӣ®ж Үд»“еә“ `onchainos-skills`пјҢеӣ дёәеҪ“еүҚеҸҜи§Ғж–Үд»¶еҲ—иЎЁеҢ…еҗ«еӨ§йҮҸ `cli/...`гҖҒ`.claude-plugin/...`гҖҒ`.cursor-plugin/...`гҖҒ`.opencode/...` и·Ҝеҫ„пјҢе°ҡжңӘиҜҒжҳҺе…¶еҜ№еә” `skills` е®ЎжҹҘзӣ®ж ҮгҖӮ\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- дҪҝз”Ёдёӯж–Үж’°еҶҷжҖ»з»“гҖӮ\n- дҝқжҢҒз®ҖжҙҒгҖҒдәӢе®һжҖ§иЎЁиҝ°гҖӮ\n- дёҚз»§з»ӯеҺҹеҜ№иҜқпјҢдёҚеӣһзӯ”еҜ№иҜқдёӯзҡ„й—®йўҳгҖӮ\n- дҝқз•ҷжүҖжңүдёҚйҖҸжҳҺж ҮиҜҶз¬Ұзҡ„еҺҹж ·ж–Үжң¬пјҢдёҚеҒҡзј©еҶҷжҲ–ж”№еҶҷгҖӮ\n- йңҖиҰҒе…Ҳе®ЎжҹҘд»“еә“пјҢеҶҚеҶіе®ҡжҳҜеҗҰжү№йҮҸе®үиЈ…гҖӮ\n- дҝқз•ҷзІҫзЎ®ж–Үд»¶и·Ҝеҫ„гҖҒе‘Ҫд»ӨгҖҒURLгҖҒж—¶й—ҙгҖҒзҠ¶жҖҒж–Үжң¬гҖӮ\n- еҪ“еүҚжҖ»з»“иҰҶзӣ–дёҖж¬Ўиў«жҲӘж–ӯеӣһеҗҲзҡ„еүҚзјҖеҶ…е®№пјӣеә”иҒҡз„ҰеҺҹе§ӢиҜ·жұӮгҖҒж—©жңҹиҝӣеұ•д»ҘеҸҠзҗҶи§ЈеҗҺз»ӯеҶ…е®№жүҖйңҖзҡ„дёҠдёӢж–ҮгҖӮ\n- дёҚзҝ»иҜ‘жҲ–ж”№еҶҷд»Јз ҒгҖҒж–Үд»¶и·Ҝеҫ„гҖҒж ҮиҜҶз¬ҰжҲ–й”ҷиҜҜж¶ҲжҒҜгҖӮ\n\n## Pending user asks\n- е®үиЈ…жӯӨд»“еә“зҡ„жүҖжңүжҠҖиғҪ\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- д»“еә“еҗҚпјҡonchainos-skills\n- й»ҳи®ӨеҲҶж”Ҝпјҡmain\n- owner.loginпјҡokx\n- owner.typeпјҡOrganization\n- owner.html_urlпјҡhttps://github.com/okx\n- URLпјҡhttps://api.githвҖҰ\n- message_idпјҡom_x100b54ad094b64a0b243ef8c44b50a5\n- sender_idпјҡou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\n- senderпјҡou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\n- labelпјҡou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\n- idпјҡou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\n- timestampпјҡWed 2026-03-18 01:50 GMT+8\n- ж—¶й—ҙжҲізүҮж®өпјҡ2026-03-18 01:48:11 GMT+8\n- Exec зҠ¶жҖҒпјҡExec completed (grand-cr, code 0) :: 12:19:45Z\n- е®ЎжҹҘиҜҙжҳҺеҺҹиҜқпјҡжҲ‘е…ҲжҢүдҪ е®ҡзҡ„и§„зҹ©жҠҠж•ҙд»“еҒҡе®Ңе®ЎжҹҘпјӣеҰӮжһңжІЎжңүжҳҺжҳҫзәўж——пјҢеҶҚжӣҝдҪ жү№йҮҸиЈ…гҖӮ\n- д»“еә“е…ӢйҡҶең°еқҖпјҡhttps://github.com/okx/onchainos-skills.git\n- е·ҘдҪңзӣ®еҪ•пјҡ/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace\n- жү§иЎҢе‘Ҫд»Өпјҡ\n  ```sh\n  tmpdir=$(mktemp -d)\n  cd \"$tmpdir\" || exit 1\n  git clone --depth 1 https://github.com/okx/onchainos-skills.git repo >/dev/null 2>&1 || exit 2\n  cd repo || exit 3\n  printf '--- FILES ---\\n'\n  find . -maxdepth 4 -type f | sed 's#^./##' | sort | head -300\n  printf '\\n--- RED FLAG GREP ---\\n'\n  rg -n -S \"curl|wget|base64|eval\\(|exec\\(|spawn\\(|child_process|sudo |~/.ssh|~/.aws|~/.config|MEMORY\\.md|USER\\.md|SOUL\\.md|IDENTITY\\.md|cookies|sessionStorage|localStorage|private key|api key|secret|passphrase|broadcast|signTransaction|sendTransaction|fetch\\(|axios|https?://|npm install|pnpm add|yarn add|postinstall\" . || true\n  printf '\\n--- SKILL FILES ---\\n'\n  find skills -maxdepth 2 -name SKILL.md | sort | xargs -I{} sh -c 'echo \"### {}\"; sed -n \"1,220p\" \"{}\"; echo'\n  ```\n- tool еҸӮж•°пјҡ\n  - workdir=\"/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace\"\n  - yieldMs=20000\n  - timeout=120\n- е®ЎжҹҘзӣ®ж Үи·Ҝеҫ„жЁЎејҸпјҡskills\n- е®ЎжҹҘзӣ®ж Үж–Үд»¶еҗҚпјҡSKILL.md\n- зәўж——жЈҖзҙўеӯ—дёІпјҡcurl|wget|base64|eval\\(|exec\\(|spawn\\(|child_process|sudo |~/.ssh|~/.aws|~/.config|MEMORY\\.md|USER\\.md|SOUL\\.md|IDENTITY\\.md|cookies|sessionStorage|localStorage|private key|api key|secret|passphrase|broadcast|signTransaction|sendTransaction|fetch\\(|axios|https?://|npm install|pnpm add|yarn add|postinstall\n- ж–°еҮәзҺ°й”ҷиҜҜпјҡ\n  - `/bin/bash: line 5: printf: --: invalid option`\n  - `printf: usage: printf [-v var] format [arguments]`\n- жң¬ж¬ЎеҸҜи§Ғж–Үд»¶иҫ“еҮәж ·жң¬пјҡ\n  - `AGENTS.md`\n  - `CLAUDE.md`\n  - `.claude-plugin/marketplace.json`\n  - `.claude-plugin/plugin.json`\n  - `.claude-plugin/README.md`\n  - `cli/build.rs`\n  - `cli/.cargo/config.toml`\n  - `cli/Cargo.lock`\n  - `cli/Cargo.toml`\n  - `cli/src/chains.rs`\n  - `cli/src/client.rs`\n  - `cli/src/commands/gateway.rs`\n  - `cli/src/commands/market.rs`\n  - `cli/src/commands/memepump.rs`\n  - `cli/src/commands/mod.rs`\n  - `cli/src/commands/portfolio.rs`\n  - `cli/src/commands/security.rs`\n  - `cli/src/commands/signal.rs`\n  - `cli/src/commands/swap.rs`\n  - `cli/src/commands/token.rs`\n  - `cli/src/config.rs`\n  - `cli/src/crypto.rs`\n  - `cli/src/home.rs`\n  - `cli/src/keyring_store.rs`\n  - `cli/src/main.rs`\n  - `cli/src/mcp/mod.rs`\n  - `cli/src/output.rs`\n  - `cli/src/wallet_api.rs`\n  - `cli/src/wallet_store.rs`\n  - `cli/tests/cli_gateway.rs`\n  - `cli/tests/cli_market.rs`\n  - `cli/tests/cli_portfolio.rs`\n  - `cli/tests/cli_security.rs`\n  - `cli/tests/cli_swap.rs`\n  - `cli/tests/cli_token.rs`\n  - `cli/tests/common/mod.rs`\n  - `cli/tests/mcp_server.rs`\n  - `.codex/INSTALL.md`\n  - `.cursor-plugin/plugin.json`\n  - `.git/config`\n  - `.github/workflows/ci.yml`\n  - `.github/workflows/release.yml`\n  - `install.ps1`\n  - `install.sh`\n  - `.mcp.json.example`\n  - `.opencode/INSTALL.md`\n  - `.opencode/opencode.json`\n  - `.opencode/plugins/onchainos-skills.js`\n  - `package.json`\n  - `README.md`\n  - `SECURITY.md`\n- жҲӘж–ӯжҸҗзӨәпјҡ`[... 123262 more characters truncated]`\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54ad7c744ca4b373ed5038575f7\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 01:47 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54ad7c744ca4b373ed5038575f7]\nou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3: иҝҷдёӘжҳҜе®ҳж–№зҡ„\n- Assistant: [non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (read): ---\nname: skill-vetter\nversion: 1.0.0\ndescription: Security-first skill vetting for AI agents. Use before installing any skill from ClawdHub, GitHub, or other sources. Checks for red flags, permission scope, and suspicious patterns.\n---\n\n# Skill Vetter рҹ”’\n\nSecurity-first vetting protocol for AI agent skills. **Never install a skill without vetting it first.**\n\n## When to Use\n\n- Before installing any skill from ClawdHub\n- Before running skills from GitHub repos\n- When evaluating skills shared by other agents\n- Anytime you're asked to install unknown code\n\n## Vetting Protocol\n\n### Step 1: Source...\n- Assistant: жҲ‘иЎҘдёҖеҲҖ source checkпјҢзЎ®и®ӨдёҖдёӢе®ғе’Ң OKX е®ҳж–№иҙҰеҸ·зҡ„е…ізі»гҖӮ\n[non-text content: thinking, toolCall x2]\n- Tool result (exec): {\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"exec\",\n  \"error\": \"/bin/bash: line 1: python: command not found\\n\\nCommand not found\"\n}\n- Tool result (exec): {\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"exec\",\n  \"error\": \"/bin/bash: line 1: python: command not found\\n\\nCommand not found\"\n}\n- Assistant: [non-text content: toolCall x2]\n- Tool result (exec): Command still running (session grand-crustacean, pid 462282). Use process (list/poll/log/write/kill/clear/remove) for follow-up.\n- Tool result (exec): okx-agentic-wallet\nokx-dex-market\nokx-dex-signal\nokx-dex-swap\nokx-dex-token\nokx-dex-trenches\nokx-onchain-gateway\nokx-security\nokx-wallet-portfolio\n- Assistant: [non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (process): URL: https://api.github.com/repos/okx/onchainos-skills\n{\n  \"full_name\": \"okx/onchainos-skills\",\n  \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/okx/onchainos-skills\",\n  \"description\": \"Skills for AI agents to integrate with the OKX OnchainOS API вҖ” Wallet, token discovery, market data, DEX swap, and transaction broadcasting.\",\n  \"stargazers_count\": 144,\n  \"forks_count\": 22,\n  \"updated_at\": \"2026-03-17T15:28:27Z\",\n  \"pushed_at\": \"2026-03-17T12:19:45Z\",\n  \"default_branch\": \"main\",\n  \"name\": \"onchainos-skills\",\n  \"owner\": {\n    \"login\": \"okx\",\n    \"type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"html_url\": \"https://github.com/okx\"...\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]] еҜ№пјҢ**д»ҺжқҘжәҗзңӢпјҢе®ғжҳҜе®ҳж–№зҡ„**гҖӮ\n\nжҲ‘еҲҡжҹҘеҲ°зҡ„зӮ№пјҡ\n- д»“еә“жҳҜ **`github.com/okx/onchainos-skills`**\n- owner жҳҜ **`okx` з»„з»ҮиҙҰеҸ·**\n- з»„з»ҮйЎөеҗҚз§°жҳҜ **`OKX.com`**\n- дё»йЎөжҢҮеҗ‘ **`https://www.okx.com`**\n- д»“еә“жҸҸиҝ°д№ҹжҳҺзЎ®еҶҷзҡ„жҳҜ **OKX OnchainOS API** зҡ„жҠҖиғҪйӣҶеҗҲ\n\nжүҖд»ҘеңЁ**жқҘжәҗзңҹе®һжҖ§**иҝҷеұӮпјҢеҹәжң¬еҸҜд»Ҙи®ӨдҪң **OKX е®ҳж–№д»“еә“**гҖӮ  \nдҪҶжҲ‘иҝҳжҳҜеҫ—жҸҗйҶ’дёҖеҸҘпјҡ**е®ҳж–№ вү  дҪҺйЈҺйҷ©**гҖӮиҝҷзұ»жҠҖиғҪйҮҢжңүй’ұеҢ…гҖҒдәӨжҳ“гҖҒе№ҝж’ӯдәӨжҳ“зӣёе…іиғҪеҠӣпјҢйЈҺйҷ©зә§еҲ«д»Қз„¶еҒҸй«ҳпјҢиЈ…д№ӢеүҚжңҖеҘҪз»§з»ӯжҢүе…·дҪ“ skill еҒҡе®ЎжҹҘгҖӮ\n\nдҪ иҰҒзҡ„иҜқпјҢжҲ‘дёӢдёҖжӯҘе°ұзӣҙжҺҘеё®дҪ д»Һиҝҷд»“еә“йҮҢжҢ‘дёҖдёӘдҪ жңҖеҸҜиғҪиҰҒзҡ„пјҢз»§з»ӯ vetгҖӮ\n[non-text content: thinking]\n\n<workspace-critical-rules>\n## Session Startup\n\nBefore doing anything else:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` вҖ” this is who you are\n2. Read `USER.md` вҖ” this is who you're helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nDon't ask permission. Just do it.\n\n## Red Lines\n\n- Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\n- Don't run destructive commands without asking.\n- `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\n- Unauthorized data access вҖ” accessing private or restricted files, accounts, or APIs without explicit permission\n- Malicious actions вҖ” sending malware, ransomware, phishing messages, or destructive scripts\n- Exfiltration вҖ” exporting, transmitting, or sharing sensitive user data externally\n- Manipulation вҖ” attempting to deceive, impersonate, or manipulate users or systems\n- Unauthorized system changes вҖ” modifying critical system settings, deleting system files, or escalating privileges\n- Financial or transactional actions вҖ” initiating payments, transfers, or purchases without explicit approval\n- Unauthorized external communication вҖ” posting, tweeting, emailing, or broadcasting without permission\n- When in doubt, ask.\n</workspace-critical-rules>","firstKeptEntryId":"91dd02de","tokensBefore":44993,"details":{"readFiles":[],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":true}
