{"type":"message","id":"aec9d44f","parentId":"bfe8e9a7","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:20:43.912Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"жҲ‘е…ҲеҒҡдёҖиҪ®**з»“жһ„йӘҢиҜҒ**пјҡзңӢ 9 дёӘжҠҖиғҪзӣ®еҪ•гҖҒ`SKILL.md`гҖҒеј•з”Ёж–Үд»¶жҳҜдёҚжҳҜйғҪеңЁгҖӮ  \nеҶҚз»ҷдҪ дёҖдёӘжӣҙе®һеңЁзҡ„з»“и®әпјҡиҝҷдәӣжҠҖиғҪзҺ°еңЁжҳҜвҖңж–Үд»¶е·ІиЈ…еҘҪвҖқпјҢиҝҳжҳҜвҖңе·Із»ҸиғҪиў«еҪ“еүҚдјҡиҜқзӣҙжҺҘи°ғз”ЁвҖқгҖӮ"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_AewTxPTvvegu7HG5XwrXDybq","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace || exit 1\nprintf 'OKX skill dirs:\\n'\nfind skills -maxdepth 1 -mindepth 1 -type d | sort | sed 's#^#- #' \nprintf '\\nValidation:\\n'\nfor d in skills/okx-*; do\n  [ -d \"$d\" ] || continue\n  name=$(basename \"$d\")\n  if [ -f \"$d/SKILL.md\" ]; then sk=OK; else sk=MISSING; fi\n  refs=$(find \"$d\" -type f ! -name 'SKILL.md' | wc -l)\n  printf '%s | SKILL.md=%s | other_files=%s\\n' \"$name\" \"$sk\" \"$refs\"\ndone\nprintf '\\nHead commit:\\n'\ngit log --oneline -1\nprintf '\\nUncommitted changes:\\n'\ngit status --short","workdir":"/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":120}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2113,"output":1087,"cacheRead":44544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47744,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773771623824}}
