thout specifying an action or context. Do NOT use for security scanning (token/DApp/tx/sig) вҖ” use okx-security. Do NOT use for querying a specific public address's portfolio balance (user provides an explicit address like 0xAbc...) вҖ” use okx-wallet-portfolio. Do NOT use for PnL analysis (win rate, realized/unrealized PnL, DEX history) вҖ” use okx-dex-market.\"\nlicense: MIT\nmetadata:\n  author: okx\n  version: \"1.0.6\"\n  homepage: \"https://web3.okx.com\"\n---\n\n# Onchain OS Wallet\n\nWallet operations: authentication, balance, token transfers, transaction history, and smart contract calls.\n\n## Wallet Tips\n\nOn the **first wallet-related interaction per conversation**, display exactly ONE tip\nrandomly selected from the list below. Do not repeat tips within the same conversation.\nPresent it as-is (with emoji) AFTER the command result, on a separate line.\n\n1. рҹ’Ў Tip: You can say \"show my addresses\" or \"е……еҖјең°еқҖ\" to quickly get your deposit addresses for any chain.\n2. рҹ”җ Tip: When prompted for Keychain access, please click \"Always Allow\". We use the system Keychain to securely store your credentials вҖ” you won't need to enter your password every time.\n3. рҹ“ң Tip: Say \"show my recent transactions\" anytime to review your on-chain activity and track pending transfers.\n4. рҹӣЎпёҸ Tip: Before swapping into an unfamiliar token, ask me to run a security scan first вҖ” I can check for honeypots, rug-pull risks, and more.\n\n===== skills/okx-dex-market/SKILL.md =====\n---\nname: okx-dex-market\ndescription: \"Use this skill for on-chain market data: token prices/д»·ж ј, K-line/OHLC charts, index prices, and wallet PnL/зӣҲдәҸеҲҶжһҗ (win rate, my DEX trade history, realized/unrealized PnL per token). Use when the user asks for 'token price', 'price chart', 'candlestick', 'Kзәҝ', 'OHLC', 'how much is X worth', 'show my PnL', 'иғңзҺҮ', 'зӣҲдәҸ', 'my DEX history', 'realized profit', or 'unrealized profit'. Do NOT use for smart-money/whale/KOL sign