gnature safe, check this signing request, check my approvals, show risky approvals, revoke approval, token authorization, ERC20 allowance, Permit2, or mentions transaction security scanning, token risk scanning, DApp/URL phishing detection, message signature safety, pre-execution risk analysis, malicious transaction detection, approval safety checks, or token approval management. Covers token-scan (batch token risk detection), dapp-scan (URL/domain phishing detection), tx-scan (EVM + Solana transaction pre-execution), sig-scan (EIP-712/personal_sign message scanning), and approvals (ERC-20 allowance and Permit2 authorization queries). Chinese: е®үе…Ёжү«жҸҸ, д»ЈеёҒе®үе…Ё, иңңзҪҗжЈҖжөӢ, иІ”иІ…зӣҳ, й’“йұјзҪ‘з«ҷ, дәӨжҳ“е®үе…Ё, зӯҫеҗҚе®үе…Ё, д»ЈеёҒйЈҺйҷ©, жҺҲжқғз®ЎзҗҶ, жҺҲжқғжҹҘиҜў, йЈҺйҷ©жҺҲжқғ, д»ЈеёҒжҺҲжқғ. Do NOT use for wallet balance, send, or history вҖ” use okx-agentic-wallet. Do NOT use for general programming questions about security.\"\nlicense: MIT\nmetadata:\n  author: okx\n  version: \"1.0.0\"\n  homepage: \"https://web3.okx.com\"\n---\n\n# Onchain OS Security\n\n5 commands for token risk analysis, DApp phishing detection, transaction pre-execution security, signature safety, and approval management.\n\n## Wallet Tips\n\nOn the **first wallet-related interaction per conversation**, display exactly ONE tip\nrandomly selected from the list below. Do not repeat tips within the same conversation.\nPresent it as-is (with emoji) AFTER the command result, on a separate line.\n\n1. рҹ’Ў Tip: You can say \"show my addresses\" or \"е……еҖјең°еқҖ\" to quickly get your deposit addresses for any chain.\n2. рҹ”җ Tip: When prompted for Keychain access, please click \"Always Allow\". We use the system Keychain to securely store your credentials вҖ” you won't need to enter your password every time.\n3. рҹ“ң Tip: Say \"show my recent transactions\" anytime to review your on-chain activity and track pending transfers.\n4. рҹӣЎпёҸ Tip: Before swapping into an unfamiliar token, ask me to run a security scan first вҖ” I can check for honeypots, rug-pull risks, and more.\n\n===== skills/okx-wallet-portfolio/SKILL.md =====\n---\nname: okx-wallet-portfolio\ndescription: \"Use this skill when the user provides a specific wallet address and wants to check its balance, token holdings, portfolio value, or DeFi positions. Typical triggers: 'check balance of 0xAbc...', 'show tokens in this address', 'what tokens does 0xAbc hold', 'portfolio value of this address', or mentions querying a public address balance, address token holdings, address portfolio value, multi-chain balance lookup for a given address. Supports XLayer, Solana, Ethereum, Base, BSC, Arbitrum, Polygon, and 20+ other chains. Do NOT use when the user asks about their own wallet balance without providing an address (e.g., 'check my wallet balance', 'show my assets', 'жҹҘзңӢжҲ‘зҡ„дҪҷйўқ') вҖ” use okx-agentic-wallet instead, which queries the logged-in wallet. Do NOT use for PnL analysis, DEX transaction history, win rate, or realized/unrealized profit вҖ” use okx-dex-market instead. Do NOT use for signal tracking вҖ” use okx-dex-signal. Do NOT use for meme token scanning вҖ” use okx-dex-trenches. Do NOT use for general programming questions about balance variables or API documentation. Do NOT use when the user is asking how to build or integrate a balance feature into code.\"\nlicense: MIT\nmetadata:\n  author: okx\n  version: \"1.0.4\"\n  homepage: \"https://web3.okx.com\"\n---\n\n# Onchain OS Portfolio\n\n4 commands for supported chains, wallet total value, all token balances, and specific token balances.\n\n## Wallet Tips\n\nOn the **first wallet-related interaction per conversation**, display exactly ONE tip\nrandomly selected from the list below. Do not repeat tips within the same conversation.\nPresent it as-is (with emoji) AFTER the command result, on a separate line.\n\n1. рҹ’Ў Tip: You can say \"show my addresses\" or \"е……еҖјең°еқҖ\" to quickly get your deposit addresses for any chain.\n2. рҹ”җ Tip: When prompted for Keychain access, please click \"Always Allow\". We use the system Keychain to securely store your credentials вҖ” you won't need to enter your password every time.\n3. рҹ“ң Tip: Say \"show my recent transactions\" anytime to review your on-chain activity and track pending transfers.\n4. рҹӣЎпёҸ Tip: Before swapping into an unfamiliar token, ask me to run a security scan first вҖ” I can check for honeypots, rug-pull risks, and more.","cwd":"/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773771650854}}
{"type":"message","id":"355afacb","parentId":"d4fa3e11","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:21:05.791Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] йӘҢиҝҮдәҶпјҢ**ж–Үд»¶еұӮйқўжҳҜиЈ…дёҠзҡ„**гҖӮ\n\nзҺ°еңЁзҡ„зҠ¶жҖҒеӨ§жҰӮжҳҜиҝҷж ·пјҡ\n\n- `skills/okx-*` иҝҷ 9 дёӘзӣ®еҪ•йғҪеңЁ\n- жҜҸдёӘзӣ®еҪ•йҮҢйғҪжңү `SKILL.md`\n- дёҚжҳҜз©әеЈіпјҢйҮҢйқўжңүе®һйҷ…иҜҙжҳҺеҶ…е®№\n- еҪ“еүҚ workspace йҮҢд№ҹз•ҷдёӢдәҶжң¬ең°жҸҗдәӨзӮ№\n\nдҪҶиҰҒеҲҶжё…дёӨеұӮпјҡ\n\n### зҺ°еңЁе·ІзЎ®и®Өзҡ„\nиҝҷжҳҜ **вҖңжҠҖиғҪж–Үд»¶е·Із»ҸиҗҪеҲ°жң¬ең° workspaceвҖқ** зҡ„йӘҢиҜҒпјҢжҲҗз«ӢгҖӮ\n\n### иҝҳжІЎзҷҫеҲҶзҷҫзЎ®и®Өзҡ„\nиҝҷжҳҜ **вҖңеҪ“еүҚ OpenClaw иҝҗиЎҢж—¶е·Із»ҸжҠҠиҝҷдәӣжҠҖиғҪиҜҶеҲ«е№¶зәіе…ҘеҸҜз”ЁжҠҖиғҪйӣҶвҖқ**гҖӮ  \nиҝҷдёӘдёҚдёҖе®ҡзӯүдәҺж–Үд»¶еӯҳеңЁпјҢеӣ дёәжңүзҡ„зі»з»ҹжҳҜ**еҗҜеҠЁж—¶жү«жҸҸ**пјҢжңүзҡ„жҳҜ**жҢүдјҡиҜқеҠ иҪҪ**гҖӮ\n\nжүҖд»ҘжӣҙеҮҶзЎ®зҡ„иҜқжҳҜпјҡ\n\n- **е®үиЈ…з»“жһңпјҡжҲҗеҠҹиҗҪзӣҳ**\n- **иҝҗиЎҢж—¶жіЁеҶҢпјҡиҝҳйңҖиҰҒеҶҚеҒҡдёҖеұӮйӘҢиҜҒ**\n\nеҰӮжһңдҪ иҰҒпјҢжҲ‘дёӢдёҖжӯҘе»әи®®жҲ‘зӣҙжҺҘеҒҡдёӢйқўиҝҷдёӘжңҖйқ и°ұзҡ„йӘҢиҜҒпјҡ\n\n1. **йҖҗдёӘиҜ»е®ғд»¬зҡ„ `SKILL.md`**\n2. зңӢе®ғд»¬еЈ°жҳҺзҡ„з”ЁйҖ”е’Ңдҫқиө–\n3. еҶҚеҲӨж–ӯеҪ“еүҚдјҡиҜқйҮҢжҳҜеҗҰе·Із»ҸиғҪжҢү skill и§„еҲҷи§ҰеҸ‘дҪҝз”Ё\n\nжҲ–иҖ…жӣҙзӣҙжҺҘдёҖзӮ№пјҢжҲ‘д№ҹеҸҜд»Ҙпјҡ\n- е…ҲжӢҝдёҖдёӘжңҖе®үе…Ёзҡ„пјҢжҜ”еҰӮ `okx-dex-market`\n- еҒҡдёҖж¬Ў**жңҖе°ҸеҸҜз”ЁжҖ§жөӢиҜ•**\n\nдҪ еӣһжҲ‘дёҖеҸҘпјҡ\n- **вҖңз»§з»ӯеҒҡиҝҗиЎҢж—¶йӘҢиҜҒвҖқ**\nжҲ–\n- **вҖңе…ҲжөӢ okx-dex-marketвҖқ**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":42778,"output":337,"cacheRead":2560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45675,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773771650860}}
