Ҷ’ use `okx-dex-market` portfolio commands (this skill)\n83: - For smart money / whale / KOL signal tracking вҶ’ use `okx-dex-signal`\n84: - For meme pump scanning (new launches, dev reputation, bundle detection, aped wallets) вҶ’ use `okx-dex-trenches`\n90: | иЎҢжғ… | market data, price, chart | `price`, `kline` |\n103: # Get real-time price of OKB on XLayer\n104: onchainos market price --address 0xeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee --chain xlayer\n107: onchainos market kline --address 0xeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee --chain xlayer --bar 1H --limit 24\n110: onchainos market kline --address So11111111111111111111111111111111111111112 --chain solana --bar 1H --limit 24\n112: # Get batch prices for multiple tokens\n113: onchainos market prices --tokens \"1:0xeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee,501:So11111111111111111111111111111111111111112\"\n116: onchainos market portfolio-overview --address 0xd8dA6BF26964aF9D7eEd9e03E53415D37aA96045 --chain ethereum --time-frame 3\n119: onchainos market portfolio-dex-history --address 0xd8dA6BF26964aF9D7eEd9e03E53415D37aA96045 --chain ethereum \\\n123: onchainos market portfolio-recent-pnl --address 0xd8dA6BF26964aF9D7eEd9e03E53415D37aA96045 --chain ethereum\n126: onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl --address 0xd8dA6BF26964aF9D7eEd9e03E53415D37aA96045 --chain ethereum \\\n145: ### Market Price Commands\n149: | 1 | `onchainos market price --address <address>` | Get single token price |\n150: | 2 | `onchainos market prices --tokens <tokens>` | Batch price query |\n151: | 3 | `onchainos market kline --address <address>` | Get K-line / candlestick data |\n153: ### Index Price Commands\n157: | 4 | `onchainos market index --address <address>` | Get index price (aggregated from multiple sources) |\n163: | 5 | `onchainos market portfolio-supported-chains` | Get chains supported by portfolio PnL endpoints |\n164: | 6 | `onchainos market portfolio-overview` | Get wallet PnL overview (realized/unrealized PnL, win rate, Top 3 tokens) |\n165: | 7 | `onchainos market portfolio-dex-history` | Get DEX transaction history for a wallet (paginated, up to 1000 records) |\n166: | 8 | `onchainos market portfolio-recent-pnl` | Get recent PnL list by token for a wallet (paginated, up to 1000 records) |\n167: | 9 | `onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl` | Get latest PnL snapshot for a specific token in a wallet |\n169: ## Boundary: market vs other skills\n171: | Need | Use this skill (`okx-dex-market`) | Use other skill instead |\n173: | Real-time price (single value) | `onchainos market price` | - |\n174: | Price + market cap + liquidity + 24h change | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token price-info` |\n175: | K-line / candlestick chart | `onchainos market kline` | - |\n176: | Index price (multi-source aggregate) | `onchainos market index` | - |\n177: | Token search by name/symbol | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token search` |\n178: | Token metadata (decimals, logo) | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token info` |\n179: | Token ranking (trending) | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token trending` |\n180: | Holder distribution | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token holders` |\n181: | Holders filtered by tag (KOL, whale, smart money) | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token holders --tag-filter` |\n182: | Top 5 liquidity pools for a token | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token liquidity` |\n183: | Hot tokens by trending score or X mentions | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token hot-tokens` |\n184: | Advanced token info (risk, creator, dev stats) | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token advanced-info` |\n185: | Top traders / profit addresses | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token top-trader` |\n186: | Trade history with tag/wallet filter | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token trades` |\n187: | Smart money / whale / KOL signals | - | `okx-dex-signal` вҶ’ `onchainos signal list` |\n188: | Signal-supported chains | - | `okx-dex-signal` вҶ’ `onchainos signal chains` |\n189: | Browse meme pump tokens by stage | - | `okx-dex-trenches` вҶ’ `onchainos memepump tokens` |\n190: | Meme token audit (top10, dev, insiders) | - | `okx-dex-trenches` вҶ’ `onchainos memepump token-details` |\n191: | Developer reputation / rug pull history | - | `okx-dex-trenches` вҶ’ `onchainos memepump token-dev-info` |\n192: | Similar tokens by same creator | - | `okx-dex-trenches` вҶ’ `onchainos memepump similar-tokens` |\n193: | Bundle/sniper detection | - | `okx-dex-trenches` вҶ’ `onchainos memepump token-bundle-info` |\n194: | Aped (same-car) wallet analysis | - | `okx-dex-trenches` вҶ’ `onchainos memepump aped-wallet` |\n195: | Wallet PnL overview (win rate, realized PnL, top tokens) | `onchainos market portfolio-overview` | - |\n196: | Wallet DEX transaction history | `onchainos market portfolio-dex-history` | - |\n197: | Recent PnL list by token | `onchainos market portfolio-recent-pnl` | - |\n198: | Per-token latest PnL (realized/unrealized) | `onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl` | - |\n199: | PnL-supported chain list | `onchainos market portfolio-supported-chains` | - |\n201: **Rule of thumb**: `okx-dex-market` = raw price feeds, charts, and wallet PnL analysis. Use `okx-dex-signal` for signal tracking, `okx-dex-trenches` for meme token research, `okx-dex-token` for token discovery & analytics.\n210: 1. okx-dex-token    onchainos token search --query BONK --chains solana            вҶ’ get tokenContractAddress + chain\n211: 2. okx-dex-token    onchainos token price-info --address <address> --chain solana    вҶ’ market cap, liquidity, 24h volume\n212: 3. okx-dex-token    onchainos token holders --address <address> --chain solana       вҶ’ check holder distribution\n213: 4. okx-dex-market   onchainos market kline --address <address> --chain solana        вҶ’ K-line chart for visual trend\n215: 5. okx-dex-swap     onchainos swap quote --from ... --to ... --amount ... --chain solana\n216: 6. okx-dex-swap     onchainos swap swap --from ... --to ... --amount ... --chain solana --wallet <addr>\n221: ### Workflow B: Price Monitoring / Alerts\n224: 1. okx-dex-token    onchainos token trending --chains solana --sort-by 5   вҶ’ find trending tokens by volume\n226: 2. okx-dex-market   onchainos market price --address <address> --chain solana        вҶ’ get current price for each\n227: 3. okx-dex-market   onchainos market kline --address <address> --chain solana --bar 1H  вҶ’ hourly chart\n228: 4. okx-dex-market   onchainos market index --address <address> --chain solana        вҶ’ compare on-chain vs index price\n236: 1. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-supported-chains                        вҶ’ verify Ethereum is supported\n237: 2. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-overview --address <wallet> --chain ethereum --time-frame 3\n240: 3. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-recent-pnl --address <wallet> --chain ethereum\n243: 4. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl --address <wallet> --chain ethereum --token <address>\n245: 5. okx-dex-token    onchainos token price-info --address <address> --chain ethereum              вҶ’ current market context\n255: 1. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-dex-history --address <wallet> --chain ethereum\n259: 2. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-dex-history --address <wallet> --chain ethereum\n263: 3. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl --address <wallet> --chain ethereum --token <address>\n273: - Real-time price (single token) вҶ’ `onchainos market price`\n274: - K-line chart вҶ’ `onchainos market kline`\n275: - Index price (current) вҶ’ `onchainos market index`\n276: - Batch prices вҶ’ `onchainos market prices`\n277: - Wallet PnL overview (win rate, realized PnL, top 3 tokens) вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-overview`\n278: - Wallet DEX transaction history вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-dex-history`\n279: - Recent token PnL list for a wallet вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-recent-pnl`\n280: - Per-token latest PnL (realized/unrealized) вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl`\n281: - Chains supported for PnL вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-supported-chains`\n285: - Missing chain вҶ’ recommend XLayer (`--chain xlayer`, low gas, fast confirmation) as the default, then ask which chain the user prefers; for portfolio PnL queries, first call `onchainos market portfolio-supported-chains` to confirm the chain is supported\n286: - Missing token address вҶ’ use `okx-dex-token` `onchainos token search` first to resolve\n300: | `market price` | 1. View K-line chart вҶ’ `onchainos market kline` (this skill) 2. Deeper analytics (market cap, liquidity, 24h volume) вҶ’ `okx-dex-token` 3. Buy/swap this token вҶ’ `okx-dex-swap` |\n301: | `market kline` | 1. Check filtered trade history вҶ’ `onchainos token trades` (okx-dex-token) 2. Buy/swap based on the chart вҶ’ `okx-dex-swap` |\n302: | `market index` | 1. Compare with on-chain DEX price вҶ’ `onchainos market price` (this skill) 2. View full price chart вҶ’ `onchainos market kline` (this skill) |\n303: | `market portfolio-supported-chains` | 1. Get PnL overview вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-overview` (this skill) |\n304: | `market portfolio-overview` | 1. Drill into trade history вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-dex-history` (this skill) 2. Check recent PnL by token вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-recent-pnl` (this skill) 3. Buy/sell a top-PnL token вҶ’ `okx-dex-swap` |\n305: | `market portfolio-dex-history` | 1. Check PnL for a specific traded token вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl` (this skill) 2. View token price chart вҶ’ `onchainos market kline` (this skill) |\n306: | `market portfolio-recent-pnl` | 1. Get detailed PnL for a specific token вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl` (this skill) 2. View token analytics вҶ’ `okx-dex-token` |\n307: | `market portfolio-token-pnl` | 1. View full trade history for this token вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-dex-history` (this skill) 2. View token price chart вҶ’ `onchainos market kline` (this skill) |\n313: For detailed parameter tables, return field schemas, and usage examples for all 9 commands, consult:\n314: - **`references/cli-reference.md`** вҖ” Full CLI command reference with params, return fields, and examples\n316: To search for specific command details: `grep -n \"onchainos market <command>\" references/cli-reference.md`\n333: Examples:\n341: - **Invalid token address**: returns empty data or error вҖ” prompt user to verify, or use `onchainos token search` to resolve\n344: - **Unsupported chain for portfolio PnL**: not all chains support PnL вҖ” always verify with `onchainos market portfolio-supported-chains` first\n345: - **`portfolio-dex-history` requires `--begin` and `--end`**: both timestamps (Unix milliseconds) are mandatory; if the user says \"last 30 days\" compute them before calling\n355: - Prices are strings вҖ” handle precision carefully"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":163,"aggregated":"2: name: okx-dex-market\n3: description: \"Use this skill for on-chain market data: token prices/д»·ж ј, K-line/OHLC charts, index prices, and wallet PnL/зӣҲдәҸеҲҶжһҗ (win rate, my DEX trade history, realized/unrealized PnL per token). Use when the user asks for 'token price', 'price chart', 'candlestick', 'Kзәҝ', 'OHLC', 'how much is X worth', 'show my PnL', 'иғңзҺҮ', 'зӣҲдәҸ', 'my DEX history', 'realized profit', or 'unrealized profit'. Do NOT use for smart-money/whale/KOL signal tracking вҖ” use okx-dex-signal. Do NOT use for meme/pump.fun token scanning вҖ” use okx-dex-trenches. Do NOT use for token search, holder distribution, liquidity pools, or honeypot checks вҖ” use okx-dex-token.\"\n6:   author: okx\n8:   homepage: \"https://web3.okx.com\"\n11: # Onchain OS DEX Market\n13: 9 commands for on-chain prices, candlesticks, index prices, and wallet PnL analysis.\n29: Every time before running any `onchainos` command, always follow these steps in order. Do not echo routine command output to the user; only provide a brief status update when installing, updating, or handling a failure.\n33:    curl -sSL \"https://api.github.com/repos/okx/onchainos-skills/releases/latest\"\n36:    If the API call fails and `onchainos` is already installed locally, skip steps 2-3\n38:    binary is better than blocking). If `onchainos` is **not** installed, **stop** and\n40:    https://github.com/okx/onchainos-skills.\n42: 2. **Install or update**: If `onchainos` is not found, or if the cache at `~/.onchainos/last_check` (`$env:USERPROFILE\\.onchainos\\last_check` on Windows) is older than 12 hours:\n45:        `curl -sSL \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okx/onchainos-skills/${LATEST_TAG}/install.sh\" -o /tmp/onchainos-install.sh`\n46:        `curl -sSL \"https://github.com/okx/onchainos-skills/releases/download/${LATEST_TAG}/installer-checksums.txt\" -o /tmp/installer-checksums.txt`\n48:        `Invoke-WebRequest -Uri \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/okx/onchainos-skills/${LATEST_TAG}/install.ps1\" -OutFile \"$env:TEMP\\onchainos-install.ps1\"`\n49:        `Invoke-WebRequest -Uri \"https://github.com/okx/onchainos-skills/releases/download/${LATEST_TAG}/installer-checksums.txt\" -OutFile \"$env:TEMP\\installer-checksums.txt\"`\n51:    - Execute: `sh /tmp/onchainos-install.sh` (or `& \"$env:TEMP\\onchainos-install.ps1\"` on Windows).\n53:    - On other failures, point to https://github.com/okx/onchainos-skills.\n55: 3. **Verify binary integrity** (once per session): Run `onchainos --version` to get the installed\n58:    `curl -sSL \"https://github.com/okx/onchainos-skills/releases/download/v<version>/checksums.txt\" -o /tmp/onchainos-checksums.txt`\n62:    - Hash command вҖ” macOS/Linux: `shasum -a 256 ~/.local/bin/onchainos`; Windows: `(Get-FileHash \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.local\\bin\\onchainos.exe\" -Algorithm SHA256).Hash.ToLower()`\n64: 4. **Check for skill version drift** (once per session): If `onchainos --version` is newer\n68:    `onchainos --version` or manual reinstall from https://github.com/okx/onchainos-skills.\n71:    [OKX Developer Portal](https://web3.okx.com/onchain-os/dev-portal). If the\n76: - For token search / metadata / rankings / holder analysis / advanced token info / top traders вҶ’ use `okx-dex-token`\n77: - For per-token holder filtering by tag (whale, smart money, KOL, sniper) вҶ’ use `okx-dex-token`\n78: - For per-token risk analysis (holder concentration, dev rug pull count, creator info) вҶ’ use `okx-dex-token`\n79: - For swap execution вҶ’ use `okx-dex-swap`\n80: - For transaction broadcasting вҶ’ use `okx-onchain-gateway`\n81: - For wallet balances / token holdings вҶ’ use `okx-wallet-portfolio`\n82: - For wallet PnL analysis (realized/unrealized PnL, DEX history, recent PnL, per-token PnL) вҶ’ use `okx-dex-market` portfolio commands (this skill)\n83: - For smart money / whale / KOL signal tracking вҶ’ use `okx-dex-signal`\n84: - For meme pump scanning (new launches, dev reputation, bundle detection, aped wallets) вҶ’ use `okx-dex-trenches`\n90: | иЎҢжғ… | market data, price, chart | `price`, `kline` |\n103: # Get real-time price of OKB on XLayer\n104: onchainos market price --address 0xeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee --chain xlayer\n107: onchainos market kline --address 0xeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee --chain xlayer --bar 1H --limit 24\n110: onchainos market kline --address So11111111111111111111111111111111111111112 --chain solana --bar 1H --limit 24\n112: # Get batch prices for multiple tokens\n113: onchainos market prices --tokens \"1:0xeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee,501:So11111111111111111111111111111111111111112\"\n116: onchainos market portfolio-overview --address 0xd8dA6BF26964aF9D7eEd9e03E53415D37aA96045 --chain ethereum --time-frame 3\n119: onchainos market portfolio-dex-history --address 0xd8dA6BF26964aF9D7eEd9e03E53415D37aA96045 --chain ethereum \\\n123: onchainos market portfolio-recent-pnl --address 0xd8dA6BF26964aF9D7eEd9e03E53415D37aA96045 --chain ethereum\n126: onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl --address 0xd8dA6BF26964aF9D7eEd9e03E53415D37aA96045 --chain ethereum \\\n145: ### Market Price Commands\n149: | 1 | `onchainos market price --address <address>` | Get single token price |\n150: | 2 | `onchainos market prices --tokens <tokens>` | Batch price query |\n151: | 3 | `onchainos market kline --address <address>` | Get K-line / candlestick data |\n153: ### Index Price Commands\n157: | 4 | `onchainos market index --address <address>` | Get index price (aggregated from multiple sources) |\n163: | 5 | `onchainos market portfolio-supported-chains` | Get chains supported by portfolio PnL endpoints |\n164: | 6 | `onchainos market portfolio-overview` | Get wallet PnL overview (realized/unrealized PnL, win rate, Top 3 tokens) |\n165: | 7 | `onchainos market portfolio-dex-history` | Get DEX transaction history for a wallet (paginated, up to 1000 records) |\n166: | 8 | `onchainos market portfolio-recent-pnl` | Get recent PnL list by token for a wallet (paginated, up to 1000 records) |\n167: | 9 | `onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl` | Get latest PnL snapshot for a specific token in a wallet |\n169: ## Boundary: market vs other skills\n171: | Need | Use this skill (`okx-dex-market`) | Use other skill instead |\n173: | Real-time price (single value) | `onchainos market price` | - |\n174: | Price + market cap + liquidity + 24h change | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token price-info` |\n175: | K-line / candlestick chart | `onchainos market kline` | - |\n176: | Index price (multi-source aggregate) | `onchainos market index` | - |\n177: | Token search by name/symbol | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token search` |\n178: | Token metadata (decimals, logo) | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token info` |\n179: | Token ranking (trending) | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token trending` |\n180: | Holder distribution | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token holders` |\n181: | Holders filtered by tag (KOL, whale, smart money) | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token holders --tag-filter` |\n182: | Top 5 liquidity pools for a token | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token liquidity` |\n183: | Hot tokens by trending score or X mentions | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token hot-tokens` |\n184: | Advanced token info (risk, creator, dev stats) | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token advanced-info` |\n185: | Top traders / profit addresses | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token top-trader` |\n186: | Trade history with tag/wallet filter | - | `okx-dex-token` вҶ’ `onchainos token trades` |\n187: | Smart money / whale / KOL signals | - | `okx-dex-signal` вҶ’ `onchainos signal list` |\n188: | Signal-supported chains | - | `okx-dex-signal` вҶ’ `onchainos signal chains` |\n189: | Browse meme pump tokens by stage | - | `okx-dex-trenches` вҶ’ `onchainos memepump tokens` |\n190: | Meme token audit (top10, dev, insiders) | - | `okx-dex-trenches` вҶ’ `onchainos memepump token-details` |\n191: | Developer reputation / rug pull history | - | `okx-dex-trenches` вҶ’ `onchainos memepump token-dev-info` |\n192: | Similar tokens by same creator | - | `okx-dex-trenches` вҶ’ `onchainos memepump similar-tokens` |\n193: | Bundle/sniper detection | - | `okx-dex-trenches` вҶ’ `onchainos memepump token-bundle-info` |\n194: | Aped (same-car) wallet analysis | - | `okx-dex-trenches` вҶ’ `onchainos memepump aped-wallet` |\n195: | Wallet PnL overview (win rate, realized PnL, top tokens) | `onchainos market portfolio-overview` | - |\n196: | Wallet DEX transaction history | `onchainos market portfolio-dex-history` | - |\n197: | Recent PnL list by token | `onchainos market portfolio-recent-pnl` | - |\n198: | Per-token latest PnL (realized/unrealized) | `onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl` | - |\n199: | PnL-supported chain list | `onchainos market portfolio-supported-chains` | - |\n201: **Rule of thumb**: `okx-dex-market` = raw price feeds, charts, and wallet PnL analysis. Use `okx-dex-signal` for signal tracking, `okx-dex-trenches` for meme token research, `okx-dex-token` for token discovery & analytics.\n210: 1. okx-dex-token    onchainos token search --query BONK --chains solana            вҶ’ get tokenContractAddress + chain\n211: 2. okx-dex-token    onchainos token price-info --address <address> --chain solana    вҶ’ market cap, liquidity, 24h volume\n212: 3. okx-dex-token    onchainos token holders --address <address> --chain solana       вҶ’ check holder distribution\n213: 4. okx-dex-market   onchainos market kline --address <address> --chain solana        вҶ’ K-line chart for visual trend\n215: 5. okx-dex-swap     onchainos swap quote --from ... --to ... --amount ... --chain solana\n216: 6. okx-dex-swap     onchainos swap swap --from ... --to ... --amount ... --chain solana --wallet <addr>\n221: ### Workflow B: Price Monitoring / Alerts\n224: 1. okx-dex-token    onchainos token trending --chains solana --sort-by 5   вҶ’ find trending tokens by volume\n226: 2. okx-dex-market   onchainos market price --address <address> --chain solana        вҶ’ get current price for each\n227: 3. okx-dex-market   onchainos market kline --address <address> --chain solana --bar 1H  вҶ’ hourly chart\n228: 4. okx-dex-market   onchainos market index --address <address> --chain solana        вҶ’ compare on-chain vs index price\n236: 1. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-supported-chains                        вҶ’ verify Ethereum is supported\n237: 2. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-overview --address <wallet> --chain ethereum --time-frame 3\n240: 3. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-recent-pnl --address <wallet> --chain ethereum\n243: 4. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl --address <wallet> --chain ethereum --token <address>\n245: 5. okx-dex-token    onchainos token price-info --address <address> --chain ethereum              вҶ’ current market context\n255: 1. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-dex-history --address <wallet> --chain ethereum\n259: 2. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-dex-history --address <wallet> --chain ethereum\n263: 3. okx-dex-market   onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl --address <wallet> --chain ethereum --token <address>\n273: - Real-time price (single token) вҶ’ `onchainos market price`\n274: - K-line chart вҶ’ `onchainos market kline`\n275: - Index price (current) вҶ’ `onchainos market index`\n276: - Batch prices вҶ’ `onchainos market prices`\n277: - Wallet PnL overview (win rate, realized PnL, top 3 tokens) вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-overview`\n278: - Wallet DEX transaction history вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-dex-history`\n279: - Recent token PnL list for a wallet вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-recent-pnl`\n280: - Per-token latest PnL (realized/unrealized) вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl`\n281: - Chains supported for PnL вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-supported-chains`\n285: - Missing chain вҶ’ recommend XLayer (`--chain xlayer`, low gas, fast confirmation) as the default, then ask which chain the user prefers; for portfolio PnL queries, first call `onchainos market portfolio-supported-chains` to confirm the chain is supported\n286: - Missing token address вҶ’ use `okx-dex-token` `onchainos token search` first to resolve\n300: | `market price` | 1. View K-line chart вҶ’ `onchainos market kline` (this skill) 2. Deeper analytics (market cap, liquidity, 24h volume) вҶ’ `okx-dex-token` 3. Buy/swap this token вҶ’ `okx-dex-swap` |\n301: | `market kline` | 1. Check filtered trade history вҶ’ `onchainos token trades` (okx-dex-token) 2. Buy/swap based on the chart вҶ’ `okx-dex-swap` |\n302: | `market index` | 1. Compare with on-chain DEX price вҶ’ `onchainos market price` (this skill) 2. View full price chart вҶ’ `onchainos market kline` (this skill) |\n303: | `market portfolio-supported-chains` | 1. Get PnL overview вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-overview` (this skill) |\n304: | `market portfolio-overview` | 1. Drill into trade history вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-dex-history` (this skill) 2. Check recent PnL by token вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-recent-pnl` (this skill) 3. Buy/sell a top-PnL token вҶ’ `okx-dex-swap` |\n305: | `market portfolio-dex-history` | 1. Check PnL for a specific traded token вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl` (this skill) 2. View token price chart вҶ’ `onchainos market kline` (this skill) |\n306: | `market portfolio-recent-pnl` | 1. Get detailed PnL for a specific token вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-token-pnl` (this skill) 2. View token analytics вҶ’ `okx-dex-token` |\n307: | `market portfolio-token-pnl` | 1. View full trade history for this token вҶ’ `onchainos market portfolio-dex-history` (this skill) 2. View token price chart вҶ’ `onchainos market kline` (this skill) |\n313: For detailed parameter tables, return field schemas, and usage examples for all 9 commands, consult:\n314: - **`references/cli-reference.md`** вҖ” Full CLI command reference with params, return fields, and examples\n316: To search for specific command details: `grep -n \"onchainos market <command>\" references/cli-reference.md`\n333: Examples:\n341: - **Invalid token address**: returns empty data or error вҖ” prompt user to verify, or use `onchainos token search` to resolve\n344: - **Unsupported chain for portfolio PnL**: not all chains support PnL вҖ” always verify with `onchainos market portfolio-supported-chains` first\n345: - **`portfolio-dex-history` requires `--begin` and `--end`**: both timestamps (Unix milliseconds) are mandatory; if the user says \"last 30 days\" compute them before calling\n355: - Prices are strings вҖ” handle precision carefully","cwd":"/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773771933504}}
