on\n  - show wallet addresses / deposit / receive / top up / fund wallet\n- `okx-agentic-wallet` зҡ„жҺ’йҷӨз”ЁйҖ”дёҺжӣҝд»Ј skillпјҡ\n  - DEX swaps вҶ’ `okx-dex-swap`\n  - token search or market data вҶ’ `okx-dex-token` or `okx-dex-market`\n  - smart money / whale / KOL signals вҶ’ `okx-dex-signal`\n  - meme token scanning вҶ’ `okx-dex-trenches`\n  - non-wallet transaction broadcasting вҶ’ `okx-onchain-gateway`\n  - security scanning вҶ’ `okx-security`\n  - specific public address portfolio balance вҶ’ `okx-wallet-portfolio`\n  - PnL analysis вҶ’ `okx-dex-market`\n\n## Pending user asks\n- з”ЁжҲ·иҰҒжұӮпјҡ`ok йӘҢиҜҒjineng`\n- еҪ“еүҚжӯЈеңЁеҒҡзҡ„дәӢпјҡжҠҪжҹҘ `skills/okx-*/SKILL.md` еӨҙйғЁеҶ…е®№пјҢд»ҘзЎ®и®Ө OKX skills дёҚеҸӘжҳҜж–Үд»¶еӯҳеңЁпјҢиҖҢжҳҜе…·еӨҮеҸҜз”Ёе®ҡд№үгҖӮ\n- йҷӨдёҠиҝ°йӘҢиҜҒеӨ–пјҢжІЎжңүејҖе§Ӣд»»дҪ•е®һзҺ°гҖҒд»Јз Ғдҝ®ж”№жҲ–е®һйҷ…й’ұеҢ…ж“ҚдҪңгҖӮ\n- жІЎжңүйўқеӨ–з»Ҳз«Ҝз”ЁжҲ·иҜ·жұӮпјҢйҷӨеҹәдәҺ `skills/okx-agentic-wallet/SKILL.md` зҡ„иғҪеҠӣ/и·Ҝз”ұзЎ®и®ӨеӨ–гҖӮ\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- `om_x100b54adf8a348a0b3986f1c89a42b4`\n- `ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3`\n- `Wed 2026-03-18 02:20 GMT+8`\n- `/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace`\n- `skills`\n- `skills/humanizer-zh`\n- `skills/okx-agentic-wallet`\n- `skills/okx-dex-market`\n- `skills/okx-dex-signal`\n- `skills/okx-dex-swap`\n- `skills/okx-dex-token`\n- `skills/okx-dex-trenches`\n- `skills/okx-onchain-gateway`\n- `skills/okx-security`\n- `skills/okx-wallet-portfolio`\n- `skills/web-search-pro`\n- `SKILL.md`\n- `skills/okx-*/SKILL.md`\n- `skills/okx-agentic-wallet/SKILL.md`\n- `okx-agentic-wallet | SKILL.md=OK | other_files=1`\n- `okx-dex-market | SKILL.md=OK | other_files=1`\n- `okx-dex-signal | SKILL.md=OK | other_files=1`\n- `okx-dex-swap | SKILL.md=OK | other_files=1`\n- `okx-dex-token | SKILL.md=OK | other_files=1`\n- `okx-dex-trenches | SKILL.md=OK | other_files=1`\n- `okx-onchain-gateway | SKILL.md=OK | other_files=1`\n- `okx-security | SKILL.md=OK | other_files=4`\n- `okx-wallet-portfolio | SKILL.md=OK | other_