{"type":"message","id":"c2f0c126","parentId":"4ad6957b","timestamp":"2026-03-17T18:49:00.375Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Deciding on device approval process**\n\nI need to provide a brief answer about approving the latest device request. It seems the gateway is closed, which isnвҖҷt healthy. I could possibly use the nodes tool to handle pending approvals instead. The developer mentioned that openclaw devices can be approved via CLI, but I think using the nodes pending/approve is the better option. IвҖҷll list them first and then approve the latest without needing to ask further.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"CLI иҝҷжқЎжІЎжү№жҲҗпјҢдёҚжҳҜеҸӮж•°й—®йўҳпјҢжҳҜ **gateway иҮӘе·ұжҠҠиҝһжҺҘе…ідәҶ**гҖӮ  \nжҲ‘жҚўз¬¬дёҖж–№е·Ҙе…·зӣҙжҺҘзңӢеҫ…е®Ўжү№еҲ—иЎЁпјҢеҶҚжү№жңҖиҝ‘дёҖжқЎгҖӮ"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_oZlBycoBTv7pApHvI8ilI3fG","name":"nodes","arguments":{"action":"pending","timeoutMs":10000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":992,"output":247,"cacheRead":48256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49495,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773773333987}}
